OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched
OL,7,Finto a series of deaths at Parc Prison
OL,8,Fin , south Wales.JSix inmates are
OL,9,Funderstood to have died since the end
OL,10,Fof February at the privately-run
OL,11,Fprison, which houses more than 1,700
OL,12,Finmates.JThe prisons watchdog has
OL,13,Flaunched a probe into the deaths at
OL,14,FHMP Parc, which is run by private
OL,15,Fsecurity firm G4S and is one of the
OL,16,Flargest prisons in the UK.JTwo deaths
OL,17,Fwere reported at the prison on
OL,18,FFebruary 27. The prisoners who died
OL,19,Fwere Jason Hussey and John Rose.JG4S,
OL,20,Fthe private security firm that runs
OL,21,Fthe prison, said: "Our thoughts are
OL,22,Fwith the families and friends of the
OL,23,Fprisoners who have died recently at
OL,24,FParc. As with all deaths in custody,
OL,25,Fthe Prison and Probation Ombudsman
OL,26,Fwill investigate."
