OL,6,FOmbudsman Adrian Usher said,
OL,7,F"Naturally, I am very concerned about
OL,8,Fthe number of deaths which have
OL,9,Foccurred in such a short space of time
OL,10,Fand I offer my deepest condolences to
OL,11,Fthe family and friends of those
OL,12,Faffected. However we are not making
OL,13,Fany assumptions and we are keeping an
OL,14,Fopen mind as to whether or not there
OL,15,Fis a causal link behind these deaths."
