OL,6,FIn a 2022 inspection, 49% of surveyed
OL,7,FParc prisoners said it was easy to get
OL,8,Fhold of illegal drugs there, compared
OL,9,Fwith 32% in similar prisons. The HM
OL,10,FChief Inspector of Prisons also wrote
OL,11,Fthat self-harm levels were "high"
OL,12,Famong Parc prisoners and that there
OL,13,Fhad been five "near-fatal incidents"
OL,14,Fin the first six months of 2022.JA
OL,15,Fstudy in June 2023 found that Parc had
OL,16,F1,734 prisoners - significantly over
OL,17,Fits certified normal accommodation
OL,18,Fcapacity of 1,559 inmates.
